            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> oiled triangles</strong> to a baking tray (make sure they don't overlap!) and put the tray in the oven for 6-8 min or until lightly browned and crisp</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 3 or more? Use 2 trays!</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
