    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Peel your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel and quarter your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Drain the <strong>ancho chilli[es] </strong>and discard the stalk[s]</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
