      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>ancho chilli[es] </strong>to a<strong> food processor </strong>with the <strong>chopped tomato</strong>, <strong>peeled garlic</strong>, <strong>shallot</strong> and <strong>coriander </strong>(save some leaves for a garnish!)</p><p>Add the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lime[s] </strong>with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>sugar</strong>, <strong>salt </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Blitz until smooth<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>rojos sauce</strong></p>",
